{"tid":996224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★$4000 表格再告急！僅餘84萬份，相信下周會全部派罄！","createTime":"2019-01-26T06:16:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T09:21:46.000Z","uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e4978d1d9746a6370293b5f7b8d3081cab80a8c7","tid":996224,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:16:37.000Z","msg":"根據在職家庭津貼辦事處資料顯示，過去的周一至周四(21至24日)，已分別派發114萬份中文和約13萬份英文申請表格，即4天已派罄原先預備的100萬份中文版申請，而政府額外增印的100萬申請表，未計昨日(25日)周五的派發量，<span style=\"color: red;\">僅餘84萬份，相信下周亦會全部派罄</span>。而有關計劃的熱線在周一至周四共收17,421個查詢，以34條熱線計劃，即每條線路每日接512個電話，難怪市民「打極都唔通」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190126/bkn-20190126081649864-0126_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190126%2Fbkn-20190126081649864-0126_00822_001.html&d=kyUqZPIW%2FdI4el07YyYQ55ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=0a2f6f92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190126/bkn-20190126081649864-0126_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d91364fae598b2fa875f50883b234ea646623d4a","tid":996224,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:16:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffa56f2a82d9d94147b3980a800ed0158d4413d5","tid":996224,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:17:49.000Z","msg":"先達海鮮價"},{"pid":"643ff363bf6a1d0631d8a11b1a20bb8ff1eb561a","tid":996224,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:18:19.000Z","msg":"瘋搶"},{"pid":"c188d20ce247123c95553870b3e9d6d32f182f40","tid":996224,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20